show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Leena, working as the secretary to Sameer Singhlania under a secret identity, is deeply in love with him. When the company faces a cyber attack, she takes matters into her own hands, secretly handling the crisis while disguised as Dr. Sen. But her world shatters when she learns of Sameer’s engagement to Maya Agarwal, leaving her torn and awestruck by the unexpected turn of events.
